trans-unit.source: Provides an object model that allows you to construct activities dynamically that interface with the WF designer and runtime using <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ICustomTypeDescriptor"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 提供可讓您建構活動動態與 WF 設計工具和執行階段使用該介面的物件模型<xref href="System.ComponentModel.ICustomTypeDescriptor"> </xref>。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <xref href="System.Activities.DynamicActivity"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 建立的新執行個體<xref href="System.Activities.DynamicActivity"></xref>類別。

trans-unit.source: With <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity> you can create new activities without creating new types.
trans-unit.target: 與<xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>您可以建立新的活動，而不需要建立新的類型。</xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity> with its associated XAML support in <xref:System.Activities.XamlIntegration.ActivityXamlServices> allows new arguments to be defined in XAML and bound by the host without requiring XAML to be compiled.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>在其相關聯的 XAML 支援<xref:System.Activities.XamlIntegration.ActivityXamlServices>允許在 XAML 中定義與繫結，由主應用程式而不需要 XAML 編譯新引數。</xref:System.Activities.XamlIntegration.ActivityXamlServices></xref:System.Activities.DynamicActivity>
